// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0478 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2d27f984-c1f7-542f-b677-0d7496150ddf

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
